      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Chua Kong Sian</b>\n</p><p><b>Chua Kong Sian</b> (Kong Sian),<br />\na Singaporean computer scientist affiliated with the  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_University_of_Singapore\">National University of Singapore</a> and its former National Supercomputing Research Centre Singapore \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>. \nAs computer chess programmer, Chua Kong Sian is author of <a href=\"/Cobalt\" title=\"Cobalt\">Cobalt</a>, primary author of <a href=\"/GNU_Chess\" title=\"GNU Chess\">GNU Chess</a> Version 5 <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, \nand author of the <a href=\"/Cpp\" title=\"Cpp\">C++</a> <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> <a href=\"/Bitboards\" title=\"Bitboards\">bitboard-based</a> engine <a href=\"/index.php?title=Melee_Chess&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Melee Chess (page does not exist)\">Melee Chess</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1992_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1992 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#1995_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1995 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chua_Kong_Sian&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1992_...\">1992 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chua_Kong_Sian&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1992 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/gnu.chess/1aJgR-v6yQ0/GsK6fJM805AJ\">Post information from Gnuchess 4.0</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Chua Kong Sian</a>, <a href=\"/GNU_Chess#NewsGroup\" title=\"GNU Chess\">gnu.chess</a>, June 12, 1992</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/gnu.chess/szgmTVI1zdA/GZAmV4AnD4cJ\">Gnuchess 4.0 for DOS</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Chua Kong Sian</a>, <a href=\"/GNU_Chess#NewsGroup\" title=\"GNU Chess\">gnu.chess</a>, January 29, 1993</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/gnu.chess/ShJVY_9SbBo/NT5L3w1eUr8J\">Fix for ScoreKBNK routine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Chua Kong Sian</a>, <a href=\"/GNU_Chess#NewsGroup\" title=\"GNU Chess\">gnu.chess</a>, February 11, 1994&#160;» <a href=\"/KBNK_Endgame\" title=\"KBNK Endgame\">KBNK Endgame</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/gnu.chess/MW-OoiLQjQM/lzGy4cgFmkUJ\">KILLT &amp; HISTORY</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Chua Kong Sian</a>, <a href=\"/GNU_Chess#NewsGroup\" title=\"GNU Chess\">gnu.chess</a>, February 19, 1994</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/rec.games.chess/tfhHzePSb9Y/8fCarWZI_w8J\">Alpha-beta inconsistencies</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Chua Kong Sian</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rec.games.chess</a>, February 19, 1994 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/gnu.chess/4QmHQsr3Vw0/J1Jq8Vk6bXkJ\">Search extensions on recaptures</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Chua Kong Sian</a>, <a href=\"/GNU_Chess#NewsGroup\" title=\"GNU Chess\">gnu.chess</a>, March 22, 1994</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/gnu.chess/QakPMIS3Kp4/0k1TiPXgJ3sJ\">Bug fixes for PawnValue()</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Chua Kong Sian</a>, <a href=\"/GNU_Chess#NewsGroup\" title=\"GNU Chess\">gnu.chess</a>, March 24, 1994</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/gnu.chess/krMg3awPGLM/9JO608Qcn2QJ\">Alpha-beta inconsistencies</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Chua Kong Sian</a>, <a href=\"/GNU_Chess#NewsGroup\" title=\"GNU Chess\">gnu.chess</a>, May 20, 1994</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/gnu.chess/lYhaFoMSPEg/CzH4RecB1OQJ\">Bug in ttable.c wrt storing of mate scores</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Chua Kong Sian</a>, <a href=\"/GNU_Chess#NewsGroup\" title=\"GNU Chess\">gnu.chess</a>, May 20, 1994</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/gnu.chess/QpQFywlVh5U/rNQ9f0ErXjMJ\">Patches for eval.c</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Chua Kong Sian</a>, <a href=\"/GNU_Chess#NewsGroup\" title=\"GNU Chess\">gnu.chess</a>, May 28, 1994</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/gnu.chess/N7vYf0kapnM/GjruodFMjAQJ\">Pawn ram code in gnuchess</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Chua Kong Sian</a>, <a href=\"/GNU_Chess#NewsGroup\" title=\"GNU Chess\">gnu.chess</a>, June 18, 1994&#160;» <a href=\"/Pawn_Rams_(Bitboards)\" title=\"Pawn Rams (Bitboards)\">Pawn Rams</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1995_...\">1995 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chua_Kong_Sian&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 1995 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/gnu.chess/-2LP9t6hvwk/GmEAGdAd4msJ\">Killer moves</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Chua Kong Sian</a>, <a href=\"/GNU_Chess#NewsGroup\" title=\"GNU Chess\">gnu.chess</a>, March 21, 1995</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/gnu.chess/475SUvzBr7A/Yn80j6FWdzUJ\">Strange crashes in gnuchess fixed</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Chua Kong Sian</a>, <a href=\"/GNU_Chess#NewsGroup\" title=\"GNU Chess\">gnu.chess</a>, December 26, 1995</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/gnu.chess/UGpLeswpTSU/5UtPTsLqhB8J\">GNU Chess 5</a> by <a href=\"/Stuart_Cracraft\" title=\"Stuart Cracraft\">Stuart Cracraft</a>, <a href=\"/GNU_Chess#NewsGroup\" title=\"GNU Chess\">gnu.chess</a>, October 10, 1999</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chua_Kong_Sian&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=13005\">Enhanced Transposition Cutoff</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">kongsian</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 10, 2007 &#160;» <a href=\"/Enhanced_Transposition_Cutoff\" title=\"Enhanced Transposition Cutoff\">Enhanced Transposition Cutoff</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=20630\">Move generator</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">kongsian</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 12, 2008 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=22359\">Fruit 2.1 pruning</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">kongsian</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 15, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/Fruit\" title=\"Fruit\">Fruit</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chua_Kong_Sian&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=34202&amp;start=8\">Re: In peril what keeps you going</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">kongsian</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 09, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=34634\">Stockfish bitbase</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">kongsian</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 01, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=39123&amp;start=24\">Re: Magics</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">kongsian</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 25, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/Magic_Bitboards\" title=\"Magic Bitboards\">Magic Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=42603&amp;start=1\">Re: ICCA Journal</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">kongsian</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 25, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICCA Journal</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=53843&amp;start=4\">Re: Unique(n) (n=0..6) FEN files available for download</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">kongsian</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 12, 2016</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chua_Kong_Sian&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sourceforge.net/projects/melee64/\">Melee Chess Engine | Download Melee Chess Engine software for free at SourceForge.net</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/kongsian/\">kongsian - GitHub</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chua_Kong_Sian&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span clas